flowchart TD
    Repo[azork repository]
    Repo --> Src[src Rust crate]
    Repo --> Tests[tests integration suites]
    Repo --> Azext[azext Azure CLI extension]
    Repo --> Scripts[scripts Node tooling]
    Repo --> Assets[assets SVG icons and decorations]
    Repo --> Docs[docs documentation and atlas]
    Repo --> MemoryStore[memory-store companion crate]
    Repo --> Cargo[Cargo.toml Rust package]
    Repo --> BuildRs[build.rs build script]
    Repo --> PySetup[azext setup.py Python package]
    Repo --> PackageJson[package.json Playwright tooling]

    Cargo --> Lib[src/lib.rs library modules]
    Cargo --> BinAzork[azork binary]
    Cargo --> BinOit[azork-oit binary]
    BinAzork --> MainEntry[src/main.rs main]
    BinOit --> OitEntry[src/bin/azork-oit.rs main]

    Src --> Backend[src/backend]
    Src --> Dungeon[src/dungeon]
    Src --> Capabilities[src/capabilities]
    Src --> Memory[src/memory]
    Src --> Update[src/update]
    Src --> Oit[src/oit]
    Src --> World[src/world.rs]
    Src --> Parser[src/parser.rs]
    Src --> Secrets[src/secrets.rs]
    Src --> AzRunner[src/az_runner.rs]
    Src --> Agent[src/agent and agent_engine]

    PySetup --> AzextPkg[azext_azork commands]
    PackageJson --> ScreenshotScript[scripts/capture-real-screenshots.mjs]
    Assets --> DungeonRender[dungeon render icon assets]
    Docs --> Atlas[docs/atlas generated layers]
    MemoryStore --> NativeMemory[memory-store/src/lib.rs]
